@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam roundcorner 10

title microROS in WASM - Component Diagram (Simplified)

package "WASM Module" {
    [microROS API\nrcl/rclc] as API #4CAF50
    [Custom RMW] as RMW #2196F3
    [Minimal DDS] as DDS #FF9800
    [WASI Networking] as NET #9C27B0
}

API --> RMW : uses
RMW --> DDS : uses
DDS --> NET : uses

cloud "Network" {
    [DDS Network] as DDS_NET #FFC107
}

NET --> DDS_NET : communicates

note right of API
  **Official ROS2 API**
  • rcl_init()
  • rcl_publish()
  • rcl_take()
end note

note right of RMW
  **ROS Middleware**
  • Bridge layer
  • Connects API to DDS
end note

note right of DDS
  **Data Distribution**
  • Discovery
  • Message routing
  • Serialization
end note

